fields.name: Full Service (Conventional Oil)
fields.description:
a. New Engine Oil (Up to 6 Litres) 
b. Chassis Lubrication 
c. New Oil Filter 
d. Fluid Top-Ups 
e. Visual Inspection

½ Litre ATF Fluid, and power steering fluid
